description:
Don't miss the finale to this awesome three part event! The Oracle of Delphius storyline that was built up through 'Sonic the Hedgehog gets stuck in a hole because he's fat ' & 'Sonic the Hedgehog Goes To The Oracle of Delphius's 87th Birthday Party 'at long last reaches its crescendo...! Be there... or be square...

Are you as pumped as I am? Then why not support me on Patreon!
